1896 H818 Spalding Die Cuts - SGC Graded Set

1896 H818 Spalding Die Cut Baseball Player - SGC 20 (highest graded)
1896 H818 Spalding Die Cut Football Player - SGC 20 (3rd highest graded)
1896 H818 Spalding Die Cut Golf Player - SGC 20 (highest graded)
1896 H818 Spalding Die Cut Bicyclist - SGC 20 (highest graded)
1896 H818 Spalding Die Cut Tennis Player - SGC 20 (highest graded)

Great condition set that is normally found with numerous creases, missing body parts and/or horrible back damage from scrapbook removal. These are all relatively clean examples with 5 out of the 6 the highest graded to date.

$1400 delivered.
